  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>This heavy crossbow has a winch mounted below the stock.</em></p>\n<p>Up to 50 feet of silk rope can be wound onto the winch as a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Full-Round-Actions\">full-round action</a>&nbsp;that provokes&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Attacks-of-Opportunity\">attacks of opportunity</a>. The wound&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/equipment/goods-and-services/hunting-camping-survival-gear#TOC-Rope\">rope</a>&nbsp;can be attached to a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/equipment/weapons/weapon-descriptions/ammunition/arrow-barbed\">barbed bolt</a>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Grapple\">grappling</a>&nbsp;bolt as part of a loading action. After firing such a bolt, the wielder can use the winch to retract the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/equipment/goods-and-services/hunting-camping-survival-gear#TOC-Rope\">rope</a>&nbsp;or pull herself along the rope if the bolt is secure.</p>\n<p>When used with a barbed bolt, the winch provides a +2 bonus on grapple&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Combat-Maneuvers\">combat maneuver</a>&nbsp;checks to pull the target toward you.</p>\n<p>When used with a grappling bolt, the winch provides a +2 bonus on&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/climb\">Climb</a>&nbsp;checks.</p>",
